Howto  extracting Tweets from Hadoop HDFS using Apache Scala

Matteo Redaelli

http://www.redaelli.org/matteo/

USAGE:

sbt package

bin/spark-submit --class SparkExtractTweets  --master local[4] target/scala-2.10/extract-tweets_2.10-1.0.jar "searches/tyre/2014/12/*" OpenSource > /var/www/a.html

bin/spark-submit --class SparkExtractTweets  --master yarn-client target/scala-2.10/extract-tweets_2.10-1.0.jar "searches/tyre/2014/12/*" OpenSource > /var/www/a.html
